{"fadeType":2,"once":true,"scripts":[{"mode":1,"stopbgm":true,"sequence":[["Shiranui, the Do-It-All Shopkeeper\n\n<size=45>Chapter 6: The Shopkeeper's True Feelings (Pt 1)<\/size>",1]]},{"flashout":{"dur":1,"alpha":[0,1],"black":true},"say":"Port - Infirmary","dir":1,"bgm":"story-1","side":2,"bgmDelay":2,"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"bgName":"bg_story_room","flashin":{"delay":1,"dur":1,"alpha":[1,0],"black":true}},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"say":"At the infirmary, Shiranui is quietly lying on a sickbed.","dir":1,"bgName":"bg_story_room"},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"It's overwork, Nyaa.","actor":312010,"dir":-1,"bgName":"bg_story_room","nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"Sure enough...","dir":-1,"side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"actor":312010,"bgName":"bg_story_room","withoutActorName":true},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"It would seem that having to serve as secretary while also running the store has caused her to accumulate a lot of stress, Nyaa.","actor":312010,"dir":-1,"bgName":"bg_story_room","nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"If only I had noticed sooner...","dir":-1,"side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"actor":312010,"bgName":"bg_story_room","withoutActorName":true},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"Commander, you don't need to blame yourself Nyaa. This is just Shiranui's personality, she does everything meticulously and never asks for help from anyone.","actor":312010,"dir":-1,"bgName":"bg_story_room","nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"Even Akashi never noticed how burnt out she was, Nyaa. Her expression didn't change at all...","actor":312010,"dir":-1,"bgName":"bg_story_room","nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","paintingFadeOut":{"side":0,"time":0.5},"say":"Pipe down, dumb cat.","dir":1,"side":1,"action":[{"type":"shake","y":45,"delay":0.6,"dur":0.1,"number":1,"x":0}],"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"bgName":"bg_story_room","actor":301180},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"Patients should just quietly lie there and rest. Shiranui is way too stubborn, Nyaa!","dir":-1,"side":0,"action":[{"type":"shake","y":45,"delay":0,"dur":0.2,"number":2,"x":0}],"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"bgName":"bg_story_room","actor":312010},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"... I'm not trying to be stubborn, I just...","actor":301180,"dir":1,"bgName":"bg_story_room","nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"I'm used to having to do things all alone.","actor":301180,"dir":1,"bgName":"bg_story_room","nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"say":"The Shiranui that sat up from the sickbed still wore the same expression as ever but, compared to usual, seemed a lot more vulnerable.","dir":1,"bgName":"bg_story_room"},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"What a troublesome fellow, Nyaa...","actor":312010,"dir":-1,"bgName":"bg_story_room","nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","paintingFadeOut":{"side":0,"time":0.5},"say":"You're the last one I want to hear that from.","dir":1,"side":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"bgName":"bg_story_room","actor":301180},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"I was relieved to see that Shiranui was fine, but it was clear that things could not continue like this.","dir":1,"side":2,"options":[{"flag":1,"content":"Suggest that Shiranui should focus on one thing first"}],"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"actor":301180,"bgName":"bg_story_room","withoutActorName":true},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"……","actor":301180,"dir":1,"bgName":"bg_story_room","nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"Hmm. I'm not sure that's going to work.","actor":312010,"dir":-1,"bgName":"bg_story_room","nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"say":"Eh? Even Akashi is opposed to that idea?","dir":1,"bgName":"bg_story_room"},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"*sigh* ... This person sure is dense.","dir":1,"side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"actor":301180,"bgName":"bg_story_room","blackBg":true}],"mode":2,"fadein":1.5,"id":"BUZHIHUO6","fadeOut":1.5}